ent.\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1870434857108938e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Seine River\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"its bridges\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique backdrop\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2328}, {\"ngram\": \"a watercourse\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"a monument\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe that, around the globe, it was the magic of the City of Light that was felt \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 a magic that shines brightest when it connects with the world.\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\": \"the magic\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2499}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2508}, {\"ngram\": \"a magic\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2534}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When China hosted the Summer Olympic Games in 2008, renowned Chinese director Zhang Yimou's creation left the world in awe, with some elements becoming iconic.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2596, \"end\": 2601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999289307223, \"rank\": 6.390492875013958e-08, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2652, \"end\": 2659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9216280320934513, \"rank\": 0.08287267252635262, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yimou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zhang Yimou\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yimou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Yimou\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Summer Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2706}, {\"ngram\": \"awe\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"some elements\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure many of us remember the majestic sound of 2008 drummers all beating in unison at the Beijing Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"the majestic sound\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"2008 drummers\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"unison\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beijing Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarly, some of the moments from the opening ceremony in Paris are likely to become visual icons over time.\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2941, \"end\": 2946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1870434857108938e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moments\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2911}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"visual icons\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These pop culture icons do not divide us; rather, they bring us closer together through shared narratives and memories.\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3111, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These pop culture icons\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"shared narratives\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"memories\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anyone who watched the 1980 Games in Russia vividly remembers Misha, the Russian bear mascot, while Muhammad Ali lighting the flame at the 1996 Games in the U.S. remains a profoundly moving moment for all who witnessed it.\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3150, \"end\": 3156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999918901059189, \"rank\": 8.066235231939212e-06, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 3175, \"end\": 3180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Misha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2004796201691925e-30, \"text\": \"Misha\", \"types\": [\"Q627603\", \"Q1107\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Misha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Misha\"}, {\"begin\": 3186, \"end\": 3198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Bear\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russian bear\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Bear\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Bear\"}, {\"begin\": 3213, \"end\": 3225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999962240279623, \"rank\": 2.4113364126767053e-06, \"text\": \"Muhammad Ali\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muhammad_Ali\"}], \"noun_ph